articles.title: Elon Musk Says Future SpaceX Starship ‘Will Travel To Other Star Systems’ After Rocket’s Latest Test - Forbes
articles.description: “Starship will be on Mars within 5 years,” Musk said, adding that “a future Starship, much larger and more advanced, will travel to other star systems.”
